headline: Prediction: Caterpillar's Stock Becomes a Buy When This Key Number Turns Around
summary: The heavy machinery maker's retail sales to its end users appear to be in an uptrend.  Dealer inventory is lower than expected, indicating that sales growth is likely to follow.  This key metric below will guide the way to increased profitability for Caterpillar.
